      <title>Lust For Youth and Croatian Amor share an expanded deluxe edition of last year’s...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DU-3SYyjbny/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/637152073_18566254957012575_4729089635481467375_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=100&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzNjc0MDY1NDIwMjc5NjEzOQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=oaeu7GgPcXQQ7kNvwHiwG3q&amp;_nc_oc=Adr5gQnzTMKo7WL1-NOUm_YtBp6IT5oPPLFAVr0xblcRWUaikF6tBXY3qoBo2ZQAZn8&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=F-DDj9l7dD4HNbbuWhfnLw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwAlURJjHv2CwXjT3VkpFym37Oy-VPEB5Hkp-n5Om7ODQ&amp;oe=69C9FF46" alt="Slide 1 fra @amortheworld" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/632403743_18566254966012575_8869296219188833845_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzNjc0MDY1NjE3NDEyODY0Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=rvy6Wx8GcrEQ7kNvwFIVErR&amp;_nc_oc=AdrJXEFjqdHYIpmtQYqnzBbvrZ07lv9UrGquBDAZfH384kc09zQqrc9W9SkCi5mfttc&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=F-DDj9l7dD4HNbbuWhfnLw&amp;_nc_ss=7a3ba&amp;oh=00_Afy7Jm3mMUR39Pd5FtPt5bUYQUe1zZAG7djYvBx6qQXHig&amp;oe=69CA0987" alt="Slide 2 fra @amortheworld" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (2 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@amortheworld</strong></p><p>Lust For Youth and Croatian Amor share an expanded deluxe edition of last year’s album ‘All Worlds’. The new edition returns to the original recording sessions with two previously unreleased tracks - “Someone” and “Parasol” - extending the album’s central themes of connection, uncertainty and devotion.<br/>
<br/>
“Someone,” featuring @purientx , deepens the album’s emotional core through a longing, synth pop framework steeped in dreamy atmospheres and reverb washed textures. “Parasol” offers a counterbalance: a drifting, sun-dazed instrumental built around a Vini Reilly–inspired guitar motif, shaped by dictaphone textures, radio interference and a vocal sample of Loke Rahbek’s son singing. It functions as an interlude between worlds - reflective and suspended.<br/>
<br/>
Rather than bonus material, these tracks feel like additional fragments from the same constellation, completing the picture of ‘All Worlds’ as a hopeful, generous constellation of inner landscapes reaching outward, waiting to be received.  Listen to “All Worlds (Deluxe)” streaming everywhere now!<br/>
<br/>
Press shot by Alexander Rotondo <br/>
Cover art by @yukiinspace</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DU-3SYyjbny/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
